replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/145157_fd0a11e576c47fc6fb70834b1a121a18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F145157_fd0a11e576c47fc6fb70834b1a121a18.png&h=dc5957d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b584950db5323145ddb968bff5220ed2d84db8f","tid":780221,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有個計法要求。 Log in 返貼出黎。其實無咩用 唔知點解做保險覺得呢個好威威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔記得uwant 定discuss 以前有個post ，有人講解過：<br />\n點解保險從業員要係社交媒體不斷講到自己好勁咁，包裝mdrt 之類。<br />\n原因係買保險的人，最怕保險從業員做唔掂。一旦保險從業員接左你單保險。而佢做唔掂而唔做保險，你買的保險就會變孤兒單，而咁的單係好難搵人跟進。（因為無佣金收）"},{"pid":"f4197d493ab6173633cc6e0e6ea72face99dd221","tid":780221,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"1年就50幾萬<br />\n連續幾年就一百萬年薪左右<br />\n<br />\n係幾勁 不過而家多大陸market就唔算特別勁"},{"pid":"bd69cd4001329bb5c6223663467d3ab3f9dd58a2","tid":780221,"uid":61631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"百萬呢個字好睇你地了唔了解個佣金制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁的確有用收入既計法 剩係每間公司計法都可以好唔同"}]}